    "description": "Portfolio project for manual and automated API testing using Postman.\n\nIncludes:\n\n- GET requests\n    \n- POST requests\n    \n- PUT requests\n    \n- PATCH requests\n    \n- DELETE requests\n    \n- Environment variables\n    \n- Automated tests with pm.test()\n    \n- JSON schema validation\n    \n- Newman CLI execution",
